misconceptions.remediation_hint:
Move the prompt and `input.nextInt()` into the loop body (or repeat them inside the loop) so that each iteration reads a new guess. For example:

```java
int guess;
while (true) {
    System.out.print("Guess my number: ");
    guess = input.nextInt();
    if (guess < answer) {
        System.out.println("Too low, try again.");
    } else if (guess > answer) {
        System.out.println("Too high, try again.");
    } else {
        break; // correct guess
    }
}
```

